patterns.name: foilbass
patterns.text: jux rev $ slow 2 $ n (foldl (append) "0 3" ["0 3", "0 4", "0 5", "0 [3 6]"]) # sound "foil3" # speed 2 # crush 3 # hall 0.2 # halldelayfb 0.1 #orbit 4

patterns.name: pat
patterns.text: chop 2 $ slow (7/3) $ nToOrbit $ modNote 0 ((#lpf 500).(#lpq 0.1)) $modNote 1 ((#speed 0.5).(#psrate (disc (16) $scale 0.9 2 $ saw*2)))$ modNote 2 ((#end 1).(#speed 0.5))$ modNote 3 ((#comb 0.7).(#lbrick 0.2))$ modNote 4 ((#lpf 8000).(#hall 0.3).(#comb (disc (16) $scale 0.9 2.9 $ saw*3)).(#detune (disc (16) $scale 0.9 9 $ tri*2)).(#gain 1).(#coarse "<12 24 0 12>").(#octer 0.91).(#sustain (disc (8) $scale 0.9 3 $ rand*2)).(#speed (disc (16) $scale 0.9 3 $ saw*2 * sine))) $ n "{0 4  1 0 <4 0> 1 <4 1 [1 [2 3]]>, 4} " #s "blp1"

patterns.name: pat2
patterns.text: chop 2 $ slow (7/3) $ nToOrbit $ modNote 0 ((#lpf 500).(#lpq 0.1)) $modNote 1 ((#speed 0.5).(#psrate (disc (16) $scale 0.9 2 $ saw*2)))$ modNote 2 ((#end 1).(#speed 0.5))$ modNote 3 ((#comb 0.7).(#lbrick 0.2))$ modNote 4 ((#lpf 8000).(#hall 0.3).(#comb (disc (16) $scale 0.9 2.9 $ saw*3)).(#detune (disc (16) $scale 0.9 9 $ tri*2)).(#gain 1).(#coarse "<12 12 0 12>").(#octer 0.91).(#sustain (disc (8) $scale 0.9 3 $ rand*2)).(#speed (disc (16) $scale 0.9 3 $ saw*2 * sine))) $ n "{3 4  1 3 <4 3> 1 <4 1 [1 [2 3]]>, 4} " #s "`x`" #comp 0.5

patterns.name: fill
patterns.text: slow (7/3) $ sound "{hh:`x` ~ qahats:5 hh:8 <[ ~ qahats:5] hh:`x`*4> <hh:9*2 ~ [qahats:1 hh:6 hh:15]> [~ hh:3 <hh:`x` hh:1>], hh:`x`*2}" #orbit 3 #hall 0.01 #pan (slow 2 $ disc 8 $ scale 0.40 0.6 $ saw) #gain (slow 2 $ disc 4 $ scale 1.025 1.0405174 $ saw) #end (fast 2 $ disc 8 $ scale 0.035 0.74 $ saw) #hpf (disc 8 $ scale 135 4074 $ saw)

patterns.name: notes
patterns.text:
modulate `pat` sample numbers
modulate/mute fill params

patterns.name: patm
patterns.text: slow (14/3) $ sound "~  hit:`x`  hit:&`x`-1&?  [ ~ blp3:1] {[hithat:&`x`-1& cp:`x` <blp1:`x` cp:&`x`-1&*2>]} ~ ~"   #gain 1 #orbit 2 #hall 0.01  #lpf 9000 #comp 0.5 #shape 0.5

patterns.name: g2
patterns.text: slow `x` $sometimesBy 0.1`x` (off 0.5(slow (7/3)))$ note (scaleP "dorian""~ ~ [c3 fs3 gs3]  <~ [gs3 cs3]>" ) #s "sx7" #sustain "`y`" #gain (slow 2 $ scale 0.9812 1.0`y` $ sine1)|+|note "12" `z`

patterns.text: fast `x` $ note (scaleP "dorian" $ c2p' "<ds4 fs4 as4> <cs4 c4 f5>  <~ fs4 ~> ~  " ((scale (2) (-3) $ sine * rand ) * (scale (-2) (-2) $ saw * 2))) #s "`y`" #gain 1.081  #sustain (scale 0.1 3 $ rand * saw) #coef 0.015  #orbit 6 |+|note "`z`" #decay (scale 1 10 $ rand * saw) #dubsp 0.0002

patterns.name: g22c
patterns.text: slow 16 $ every 7 (slow (3.5/3))$ n "[c3 fs3 gs3] ~ ~ <~ [gs5 cs5]>" #sustain 0.1 #cc8 (fast 4 $ scale 0.1`x`2 0.93 $ sine1) #cc1 "0.9" #gain "0.9"  `z` |+|up `x`

patterns.name: fil
patterns.text: nToOrbit $ every 9(1 <~) $ chop 14 $ juxBy 0.2 (#speed 3 ) $  slow (`x`/3) $ n "{ ~ ~ [2 3 1 <2*2 3*2>]  ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ }"# s "`y`"  #gain 1 #speed 1 #end 0.25 #pan (disc 8 $ scale 0.35 0.74 $ rand)

patterns.name: amb
patterns.text:
slow (28/3) $ weave 16 (note (scaleP "majPent" "0 .. 4") # sound "`x`" # gain (fastcat [saw, 1, 1, 1, rev saw]))
  [vowel "o*2 i(3,8) u",
   vowel "i o u*2",
   vowel "o i [u e] a"
  ] |+|n "0"
#gain 0.81 #lpf 9000 #coarse 4 #orbit 5 #speed 1 #hall 0.1
